<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"
>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport" />
    <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta content="telephone=no" name="format-detection" />
    <title></title>
  </head>

  <body aling="center">
    <div class="logo" style="width: 100%; text-align: center">
      <img
        src="https://birthdayremember.s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/mail-logo.jpg"
        alt="birthday-remember logo"
      />
    </div>
    <div
      class="main"
      style="width: 100%; height: 100%"
      style="text-align: center"
    >
      <h1 style="text-align: center">Olá, {{username}}.</h1>
      <br />
      <p style="text-align: center">
        Obrigado por se interessar e fazer parte da nossa plataforma.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p style="text-align: center">
        Para evitar spam, pedimos para que você verifique sua conta.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p style="text-align: center">
        Para verificar sua conta basta clicar no botão abaixo:
      </p>
      <a
        href={{link}}
        style="
          padding: 1rem;
          background-color: purple;
          text-align: center;
          text-decoration: none;
          color: #000000;
          margin: 0 auto;
          display: block;
          width: 100px;
          border-radius: 4px;
        "
        >Verificar</a
      >
      <br />
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
